You can use these connectors as a pilot or beta feature to sync external data with CRM Analytics. 
HubSpot Connection (Beta) - Pull your marketing, sales, and customer service data from HubSpot into Data Manager.
Marketo Connection (Beta) - Create a remote connection using the Marketo connector to sync data from Marketo to CRM Analytics.
Snowflake VPC Connection (Pilot) - Pull your data securely from Snowflake running on AWS into Data Manager.
title: Pilot and Beta Connectors for Salesforce CRM Analytics
